    <briefdescription>
<para>Basic type: 3D line. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class represents a three-dimensional line in space. Lines are constructed from a point, <computeroutput>p0</computeroutput>, and a direction, dir. The direction is normalized in the constructor.</para>
<para>The line is kept in a parametric represention, p = p0 + t * dir. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
